{"tid":811802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴跌銀包","createTime":"2018-09-09T06:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T06:54:21.000Z","uid":179380,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7b66cc822a0f8dede849449e81d77bf2db665d","tid":811802,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"話說今日搭小巴唔小心跌咗銀包，銀包入面有大約八百蚊同幾張證件。跑去站頭搵，站長就叫我留電話，有就比電話我<br />\n又咁好彩真係搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行去小巴站果陣諗住比100～200蚊當報酬。返到小巴站攞起銀包一睇...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母攞撚咗我三百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知係唔係拎撚咗去賭<br />\n大家又覺得小巴佬問都唔問就拎走D錢又啱唔啱<br />\n正皮：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主扺撚死，當交學費啦<br />\n負皮： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小巴佬正仆街"},{"pid":"fd31667d3c1d39864bfdcd1751c5db7fdb6e5c09","tid":811802,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76149bfa1fe9cc66030b2bc8785615c21168aaa0","tid":811802,"uid":20459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"拎得番咪算好"},{"pid":"1544c0a5a279d65d1ebe99c6e14fb0690605dc6a","tid":811802,"uid":179380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76149bfa1fe9cc66030b2bc8785615c21168aaa0","tid":811802,"uid":20459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"拎得番咪算好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"你都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e592d58b6ac99007a53a7bb6b29e1142a80b07","tid":811802,"uid":72688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"一定係小巴佬攞你嘅咩柒頭<br />\n<br />\n下次扔撚咗佢都唔撚比返你 好心著雷劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a78ad3b4ae609f380a7d1fe030